 news|title= ROUTES: Flynas to start US flights in 2015|work= [[Flightglobal]]|date= 7 April 2014|url= http://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/routes-flynas-to-start-us-flights-in-2015-397891/|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140609210220/http://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/routes-flynas-to-start-us-flights-in-2015-397891/|archivedate= 9 June 2014 }}</ref>\n<!-- + -->\n<ref name=\"Saudia Arabian flight touches down in Manchester for first time\">{{cite news|title= Saudia Arabian flight touches down in Manchester for first time|first= Charlotte|last= Cox|newspaper= Manchester Evening News|date= 9 May 2014|url= http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/news/greater-manchester-news/saudia-arabian-airline-flynas-touched-7095578|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140509112816/http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/news/greater-manchester-news/saudia-arabian-airline-flynas-touched-7095578|archivedate= 9 May 2014 }}</ref>\n<!-- + -->\n<ref name=\"Saudi Arabia's flynas long-haul LCC to Europe and Asia, introducing a new low cost alternative\">{{cite news|title= Saudi Arabia's flynas long-haul LCC to Europe and Asia, introducing a new low cost alternative|work= Centre for Aviation|date= 16 March 2014|url= http://centreforaviation.com/analysis/saudi-arabias-flynas-long-haul-lcc-to-europe-and-asia-introducing-a-new-low-cost-alternative-156951|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140402012054/http://centreforaviation.com/analysis/saudi-arabias-flynas-long-haul-lcc-to-europe-and-asia-introducing-a-new-low-cost-alternative-156951|archivedate= 2 April 2014 }}</ref>\n<!-- + -->\n<ref name=\"Saudi budget airline Flynas to begin operations next month\">{{cite news|title=Saudi budget airline Flynas to begin operations next month |work=[[The Economic Times]] |date=25 July 2014 |url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/airlines-/-aviation/saudi-budget-airline-flynas-to-begin-operations-next-month/articleshow/38983424.cms |archiveurl=https